      "rationale": "A three-level mesh refinement study (coarse 4.1 M, medium 9.8 M, fine 22.3 M cells) was conducted. GCI for the area-weighted mean shear stress — the primary hemolysis driver — is 1.8% between medium and fine meshes. The medium mesh is selected as the production mesh, satisfying Gradation 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
