      "rationale": "Predicted RH values range from 0.71 to 0.94 against experimental references of 0.68 to 0.91. Mean absolute error is 4.3%, maximum deviation 11.2%, and no systematic bias is detected. All predictions satisfy RH < 1 acceptance criterion. Gradation 2 achieved."
