      "rationale": "The relative hemolysis index RH is the regulatory acceptance metric for CPB hemolysis assessment per FDA guidance. Shear stress and Lagrangian particle exposure time are computed as supporting QoIs and confirm mechanistic consistency with the Power Law hemolysis model. Gradation 2 satisfied."
